main event: A UFO sighting involving a round object the size of a baseball was reported in Waupon, Wisconsin on 6 May 1956.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 3-5 minutes,The object was low altitude and emitted light,The object was observed by 15 men,The sighting was classified as a ground-visual observation,The object disappeared moving from south to north.
sighted object: one round object, size of baseball, like a light
